## Unique Value

This project is not just a weather application.

Weather apps show raw weather values.  
Agri-Risk AI converts weather, terrain, and environmental signals into:

- Risk prediction
- Crop recommendation
- Economic insight
- Mitigation strategy
- Decision-ready agricultural intelligence

That makes it useful for real agri-business decision systems.

---

## Team Explanation Summary

In simple words:

This project takes a farm location, fetches live environmental data, processes it into 14 important agricultural features, passes it through trained machine learning models, and returns crop risks, best crop recommendation, cost, price, season, and mitigation actions.

It helps agri-companies and platforms provide better farming decisions instead of only showing raw weather data.

